    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid), over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, crumble your<strong> flat white mushrooms</strong> into the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften and brown</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once browned, reduce the heat to medium, push the mushrooms to one side and add the<strong> drained black beans</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span><strong> warm water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>10-12 min or until the mushrooms are cooked through</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the mushrooms are cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Mash the <strong>cooked black</strong> <strong>beans</strong> until smooth and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>mushroom & black bean mix</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> mushroom & black bean mix</strong> between your <strong>tortillas</strong> and top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Fold each <strong>tortilla </strong>over so you're left with<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>half moon-shaped sandwiches</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> filled tortilla</strong> to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Place a second baking tray on top of the tortilla baking tray[s] to weigh it down slightly</p><p>Put the stacked baking trays in the oven and cook for 20-25 min or until the tortillas are slightly browned and the cheese is melted \u2013 these are your<strong> mushroom & black bean quesadillas</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim and finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then grate your <strong>apple[s]</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>grated</strong> <strong>apple</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong>, add a juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>zesty slaw</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and<strong> chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) \u2013 this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/mushroom-and-black-bean-wholemeal-quesadillas-with-zesty-slaw/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once done, leave the <strong>mushroom & black bean quesadillas</strong> to cool slightly and the cheese to set</p><p>Once cooled, slice the quesadillas into triangles</p><p>Serve the <strong>zesty slaw</strong> and the<strong> chipotle mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
